"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-29-adam-peaty-reveals-heart-melting-words-son-said-missing-olympic-gold-21316557\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB starAdam Peatyshared a touching moment with his son George after a thrilling 100m breaststroke final at theParisOlympics, in which he had to settle for silver.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Team GB starAdam Peatyshared\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"a touching moment\", \"from\": 29, \"to\": 46}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 52, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 60, \"to\": 66}, {\"ngram\": \"a thrilling 100m breaststroke\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 102}, {\"ngram\": \"theParisOlympics\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 128}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old world-record holder got off to a slow start at the Paris La Defense Arena but dragged himself back into contention with 50 meters remaining in the pool.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 29-year-old world-record holder\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 204}, {\"ngram\": \"a slow start\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"50 meters\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Victory would have seen Peaty clinch a third consecutive Olympic gold - and only the second man after Michael Phelps to win the same swimming event at three successive Games.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0255554820785542e-40, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Victory\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"a third consecutive Olympic gold\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"only the second man\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"the same swimming event\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"three successive Games\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it wasn't to be for the eight-time world champion, withItaly's Nicolo Martinenghi storming home just 0.02 seconds ahead of joint-silver medallists Peaty and Nic Fink to get his hands on gold.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"score\": 0.9999999871765796, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolo Martinenghi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\"}, {\"begin\": 676, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nic Fink\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eight-time world champion\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"his hands\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics An emotionalPeaty was consoled by BBC Sport's pool-side reporterin an emotional interview shortly after the race, before joining his wife, Holly Ramsay, and family in the stands for an intimate moment.\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Flax\", \"score\": 0.9994301843634958, \"rank\": 0.0005698907521884296, \"text\": \"Holly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Flax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Flax\"}, {\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.999993092904995, \"rank\": 6.819346165290461e-06, \"text\": \"Ramsay\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Ramsay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"An emotionalPeaty\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional interview\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"an intimate moment\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'George normally goes, \\\"Daddy, are you the fastest boy?\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Daddy\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest boy\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", and I would have said, \\\"Not today\\\",' Peaty later explained.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But he says, \\\"I love you, Daddy\\\", and that's all I care about.'\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a beautiful moment of Adam Peaty with his son \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u00ba\\u00e2\\u009d\\u00a4\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008f#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/3JCRHysjdd Peaty said he had been suffering with a sore throat heading into the final, though was reluctant to use it as an 'excuse'.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What a beautiful moment\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"a sore throat\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'excuse\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I had a curveball this morning with my throat and stuff.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a curveball\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"my throat\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can train eight years for something and not feel 100 per cent on a day.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight years\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"100 per cent\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And 100 per cent costs you 0.02 and that's just the way,' he added.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"just the way\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I do not ever want that to be an excuse.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an excuse\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the cards I was dealt.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cards\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I will not be going home thinking about that, even if it feels like a hangover in the morning because of the emotions.'\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home thinking\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"a hangover\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty continued: 'Getting here was a big achievement.\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"a big achievement\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not sad at all.\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'When I touched the wall.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I truly believed I'd got it but it wasn't meant to be.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I'd won it would have been a fairytale ending.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fairytale ending\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I am not defining this whole journey back, the last 14 months, by whether I got a medal or not.'\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this whole journey\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Peaty collected and proudly displayed his silver medal on the podium,BBC presenter Clare Balding criticisedEngland's footballers for refusing to do the same after their Euro 2024 disappointment.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"his silver medal\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"their Euro 2024 disappointment\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I love this because honestly, after the final of the Euros when they [England's players] all took their medals off, I just thought, \\\"You got to a final, you performed really well, do not say this means nothing\\\".\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2403, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994173362279248, \"rank\": 0.0002852738193332504, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Euros\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"their medals\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I love the fact that Adam and Nic Fink there are clearly incredibly proud of those silver medals and will hold them up and say, \\\"Yes, I won this\\\".'\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"Adam\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"Nic Fink\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"those silver medals\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2744, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more stories\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2712}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport page\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro Sport\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2764}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest news onFacebook\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"TwitterandInstagram\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Laura Robson reveals Andy Murray's niche collection obsession at the Paris Olympics ArrowMORE:Tom Daley and Noah Williams' tear-jerking reaction to synchro diving silver at Paris 2024 ArrowMORE:How does the Olympic diving scoring system work and how many rounds are there?\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 3102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2828, \"end\": 2840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Robson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Robson\"}, {\"begin\": 2849, \"end\": 2860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.782644154474201e-35, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2923, \"end\": 2932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.79544800333831e-42, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begi